00:01:27.700 --> 00:01:31.200
=The Maid=

00:01:31.444 --> 00:01:34.144
=Episode 18=

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:49.760
Shen Yuqing.

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:52.560
The one who wants you dead

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:55.560
is your biological father.

00:01:58.760 --> 00:01:59.760
I don't have a father.

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:06.440
His Highness favors you more than me.

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:10.640
If you'd just admitted
being Shen Yuqing earlier,

00:02:11.880 --> 00:02:14.200
with Father's opportunistic nature,

00:02:14.840 --> 00:02:17.040
he might have wavered between us.

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:23.000
But you stubbornly refused
to reclaim your identity.

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:25.400
You dug your own grave.

00:02:33.600 --> 00:02:34.480
Shen Yuanjin.

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:38.720
How does it feel to lose your mother?

00:02:45.640 --> 00:02:47.000
For the rest of your life,

00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:49.960
you'll never sleep peacefully again.

00:02:53.320 --> 00:02:55.360
Lin Jifu and Madam Su

00:02:56.040 --> 00:02:57.920
will haunt you forever.

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:27.040
The Duke has arrived.

00:03:27.232 --> 00:03:32.320
The Ministers of War, Revenue,
and Justice have arrived!

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:34.760
- Xiao.
- Xiao.

00:03:39.320 --> 00:03:40.000
Xiao.

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:41.680
Outrageous!

00:03:42.880 --> 00:03:44.120
Who gave you the audacity

00:03:44.920 --> 00:03:47.000
to threaten the Prince Regent
with troops?

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.200
Xiao,

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:55.280
are you alright?

00:03:59.480 --> 00:04:00.280
Xiao,

00:04:00.880 --> 00:04:02.640
we didn't mean to offend His Highness.

00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:04.600
The troops

00:04:05.080 --> 00:04:06.720
are absolutely furious.

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:07.720
Indeed.

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:15.480
Your Highness, please calm down.

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:17.600
The Western Army's Six Loyalists

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.640
have always cherished soldiers.

00:04:20.080 --> 00:04:21.640
When they learned

00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:22.440
I was in danger,

00:04:22.440 --> 00:04:23.520
in their urgency,

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.960
they inevitably overstepped boundaries.

00:04:31.720 --> 00:04:32.520
Xiao.

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:35.000
The demoness attempted
to assassinate the Duke.

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:36.480
By law, she should be executed.

00:04:36.760 --> 00:04:38.320
The demoness caused a mutiny,

00:04:38.480 --> 00:04:39.936
threatening the nation's foundation.

00:04:39.936 --> 00:04:40.880
She deserves death.

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:41.600
Your Highness,

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:42.920
be the Empress Dowager's order,

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:43.920
we came to oversee.

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:44.600
Once it's time,

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:45.520
the fire must be lit.

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.320
Fifth Sworn Brother guards the border.

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:49.280
He's always hated evil.

00:04:50.040 --> 00:04:51.600
If he hears of this,

00:04:52.040 --> 00:04:53.680
he'll surely bring the Western Army

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:54.880
straight to the capital.

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:56.040
By then,

00:04:56.520 --> 00:04:58.640
no one could stop him.

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:10.480
With all of you present today,

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:13.360
I'd like to see for myself

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:16.680
who among you dares to rebel.

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:34.320
My lady,

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:37.040
the Duke and senior officials
have all arrived.

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.760
Don't waste this opportunity.

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:40.640
Don't worry.

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.160
I've been waiting

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:45.160
for this moment for three years.

00:05:58.720 --> 00:06:00.520
You're not watching
the secondary consort.

00:06:00.520 --> 00:06:02.200
Where are you going?

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:06.440
How does the discussion proceed
in the main hall?

00:06:07.320 --> 00:06:08.640
No matter what happens,

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:10.440
when the time comes,

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:12.240
the fire must be lit.

00:06:13.640 --> 00:06:15.400
I fear the Prince Regent's retaliation.

00:06:15.800 --> 00:06:17.560
Better confirm first.

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:21.040
Lady Zheng,

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:22.840
you're indeed the traitor.

00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:25.240
Fortunately, my father anticipated this.

00:06:26.760 --> 00:06:27.680
You shameless fool.

00:06:27.880 --> 00:06:28.720
Let me go!

00:06:30.200 --> 00:06:32.800
(No! Can't let Shen Yuanjin
take Lady Zheng.)

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:34.944
Move!

00:06:45.640 --> 00:06:46.440
My lord,

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:49.080
the rope's chafing my shoulders.

00:06:49.320 --> 00:06:50.760
Could you adjust it slightly?

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:57.480
I'm the Prince Regent's
secondary consort.

00:06:58.000 --> 00:06:59.280
His Highness still favors me.

00:06:59.960 --> 00:07:00.840
When he emerges,

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:02.720
I'll have him kill you

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:04.000
to join me in death!

00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:15.640
You won't escape anyway.

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:23.040
Fire!

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:24.480
Fire!

00:07:27.640 --> 00:07:29.600
She dares take such a risk?

00:07:29.760 --> 00:07:30.960
Hurry! Drag them away!

00:07:43.200 --> 00:07:43.840
Xiyan!

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:45.280
Save Lady Zheng!

00:07:45.960 --> 00:07:46.720
Go save her.

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:47.424
Understood.

00:08:13.400 --> 00:08:14.400
Ye Xiyan,

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:15.240
you got a death wish?

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:24.160
You're anxious?

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:26.280
Zip it.

00:08:28.360 --> 00:08:29.960
Among those you must protect,

00:08:32.040 --> 00:08:33.560
have I now joined their number?

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.400
The demoness prophecy

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:54.960
and the assassination attempt

00:08:55.520 --> 00:08:57.720
were all schemes devised by the Duke

00:08:57.920 --> 00:08:59.320
to frame Consort Ye.

00:08:59.520 --> 00:09:00.560
Preposterous!

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:03.080
Guards!

00:09:03.760 --> 00:09:05.280
Drag her out and beat her to death.

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:06.200
My lord,

00:09:08.520 --> 00:09:10.160
the Minister of Justice hasn't spoken.

00:09:10.600 --> 00:09:11.480
Must your reach extend

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:13.080
beyond your jurisdiction?

00:09:17.400 --> 00:09:18.960
The assassins were the Duke's men.

00:09:19.520 --> 00:09:20.920
To survive, Nanxing and I

00:09:20.920 --> 00:09:22.960
had no choice but serve him.

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:25.000
I've been wronged,
yet I can't get justice.

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:26.760
Your Highness,

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:30.520
honorable generals and lords,
please see through the truth.

00:09:35.880 --> 00:09:36.800
Gentlemen,

00:09:37.160 --> 00:09:38.680
you shared life-and-death bonds

00:09:38.680 --> 00:09:40.600
with my husband.

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:42.000
Does his death

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:44.560
not strike you as suspicious?

00:09:48.040 --> 00:09:49.800
The Duke's lust

00:09:50.040 --> 00:09:51.240
drove him to assault me.

00:09:51.240 --> 00:09:52.560
When my husband discovered this,

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:55.000
the Duke murdered him
with his own hands.

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:56.560
Afterward,

00:09:56.960 --> 00:09:58.960
he blamed enemy spies,

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:01.200
and then used mourning rites as pretext

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:03.800
to defile me

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:06.400
before my husband's coffin.

00:10:06.920 --> 00:10:07.640
Lady Zheng!

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:09.880
You're the wanton one

00:10:10.240 --> 00:10:11.000
who seduced me.

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:12.240
You schemed to enter

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:13.240
the Duke's Mansion.

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:15.120
You're lying!

00:10:17.440 --> 00:10:20.000
Would I abandon being a general's wife

00:10:20.760 --> 00:10:22.640
to become a wronged ghost

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:25.120
in your household?

00:10:27.280 --> 00:10:28.040
Xiao.

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:33.320
My lord,

00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:36.560
do you recall this dagger?

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:39.320
Back then,

00:10:39.960 --> 00:10:41.000
you used it

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:42.680
to kill my husband.

00:10:43.240 --> 00:10:44.080
To this day,

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:47.800
his blood stains remain.

00:11:06.960 --> 00:11:07.880
This Fishgut Sword

00:11:07.880 --> 00:11:09.400
was bestowed upon you by my father.

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:11.920
Yet you defile it with vile deeds.

00:11:14.360 --> 00:11:15.200
All these years,

00:11:15.800 --> 00:11:17.480
I'm not the only one who have suffered

00:11:18.360 --> 00:11:20.200
under the Duke's tyranny.

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:22.640
Gentlemen,

00:11:22.840 --> 00:11:24.280
you've been fighting abroad.

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:27.200
How could you know
the torment your households endured?

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:29.680
Your concubine Wu,

00:11:30.840 --> 00:11:32.600
your daughter Baozhen,

00:11:33.560 --> 00:11:35.040
and your cousin...

00:11:36.080 --> 00:11:37.560
They all fell victim

00:11:37.560 --> 00:11:40.480
to this wolf in noble's clothing!

00:11:40.680 --> 00:11:41.520
Xiao!

00:11:42.040 --> 00:11:43.120
Very well, Xiao!

00:11:48.160 --> 00:11:50.120
Madwoman.

00:11:50.360 --> 00:11:53.480
I should've silenced you sooner.

00:11:56.560 --> 00:11:57.840
Do you think

00:11:59.240 --> 00:12:01.360
I don't want to die?

00:12:04.120 --> 00:12:06.480
Long have I yearned for death.

00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:09.080
But I don't dare,

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:10.560
and I can't.

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:12.680
If I die,

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:14.520
none would clear

00:12:14.520 --> 00:12:15.920
my husband's name.

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:17.520
My death

00:12:17.920 --> 00:12:19.720
would free you

00:12:19.720 --> 00:12:21.000
to greater villainy.

00:12:28.880 --> 00:12:29.600
Your Highness,

00:12:30.520 --> 00:12:31.680
these records contain

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:33.600
years of evidence

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:35.480
against the Duke.

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:37.200
Payroll fraud,

00:12:37.880 --> 00:12:39.000
false military claims,

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:40.160
and embezzle funds.

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:43.120
Examine the Western Army's ledgers

00:12:43.280 --> 00:12:44.400
for full proof.

00:12:54.548 --> 00:12:57.120
(Evidence of the Duke's crime)

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:05.960
Gentlemen,

00:13:06.320 --> 00:13:09.080
you've been deceived all these years.

00:13:09.560 --> 00:13:10.720
I beg Your Highness

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:12.080
and everyone here

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:13.520
to deliver justice

00:13:13.520 --> 00:13:14.600
for those women,

00:13:15.280 --> 00:13:16.640
my husband,

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:17.920
and the Western Army.

00:13:31.440 --> 00:13:32.000
Hong!

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:33.680
Don't heed her ravings.

00:13:33.880 --> 00:13:36.160
Help me silence her.

00:13:38.360 --> 00:13:39.880
The Western Army's Six Loyalists

00:13:39.880 --> 00:13:41.840
were sworn to live and die together.

00:13:42.680 --> 00:13:44.800
Yet for your own selfish desires,

00:13:45.040 --> 00:13:46.440
you murdered Sixth Sworn Brother,

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:48.560
raped his wife,

00:13:48.920 --> 00:13:51.120
and violated our families.

00:13:51.840 --> 00:13:52.720
How dare you

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:53.920
claim to be our sworn brother?

00:13:53.920 --> 00:13:54.800
You beast!

00:13:56.920 --> 00:13:58.880
The Duke conspired
against an imperial general.

00:13:59.280 --> 00:14:00.440
Send him to the death cell.

00:14:01.120 --> 00:14:02.272
The chaste widow Lady Zheng

00:14:02.272 --> 00:14:03.552
bore disgrace to seek justice.

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:04.880
She is innocent.

00:14:05.640 --> 00:14:07.160
Dear Ministers, any objections?

00:14:08.480 --> 00:14:10.160
- You administer justice impartially.
- You administer justice impartially.

00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:12.200
- We accept the verdict wholeheartedly.
- We accept the verdict wholeheartedly.

00:14:12.200 --> 00:14:13.160
General of the West,

00:14:13.160 --> 00:14:14.205
Mi Hong, heed your orders!

00:14:14.920 --> 00:14:15.640
Yes!

00:14:15.760 --> 00:14:17.480
The Western Army needs
immediate leadership.

00:14:18.016 --> 00:14:18.880
You shall temporarily

00:14:18.880 --> 00:14:20.360
assume full command

00:14:20.360 --> 00:14:21.360
of the Western Army.

00:14:22.240 --> 00:14:23.560
As your command!

00:14:23.560 --> 00:14:24.800
Thanks for your fair judgment.

00:14:25.880 --> 00:14:26.800
Send the Duke

00:14:27.080 --> 00:14:28.240
to the imperial prison.

00:14:28.600 --> 00:14:29.320
- Understood!
- Understood!

00:14:31.520 --> 00:14:32.120
Hong!

00:14:32.640 --> 00:14:33.360
You can't do this!

00:14:33.840 --> 00:14:34.720
Hong, please!

00:14:35.200 --> 00:14:37.080
He seeks to weaken the Western Army!

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:37.800
Hong!

00:14:38.320 --> 00:14:39.800
Don't fall for his schemes!

00:14:42.880 --> 00:14:44.360
He deserves this.

00:14:45.400 --> 00:14:46.880
Karma has finally come.

00:14:47.680 --> 00:14:48.720
That monster!

00:14:50.040 --> 00:14:51.120
Finally apprehended!

00:14:51.640 --> 00:14:52.680
Worse than swine!

00:14:52.680 --> 00:14:53.520
Beat him to death!

00:14:53.880 --> 00:14:55.000
Kill him!

00:14:55.000 --> 00:14:55.840
I am the Duke!

00:14:56.120 --> 00:14:57.320
Dare any of you strike me?

00:14:58.560 --> 00:14:59.264
Who dares?

00:14:59.520 --> 00:15:00.384
Monster!

00:15:01.984 --> 00:15:02.624
Hit him!

00:15:03.488 --> 00:15:04.832
You brat!

00:15:05.880 --> 00:15:06.560
Hong.

00:15:07.232 --> 00:15:08.832
Sixth Sworn Brother can't rest in peace.

00:15:09.240 --> 00:15:10.080
This verdict

00:15:10.280 --> 00:15:11.720
shall bring peace to him,

00:15:11.720 --> 00:15:12.760
his wife,

00:15:13.320 --> 00:15:14.520
and our families

00:15:14.520 --> 00:15:15.520
who have suffered.

00:15:28.640 --> 00:15:29.440
Save me.

00:15:29.840 --> 00:15:31.560
Save me.

00:15:32.400 --> 00:15:33.400
Father,

00:15:33.880 --> 00:15:35.160
don't you recognize me now?

00:15:47.800 --> 00:15:48.560
You...

00:15:49.440 --> 00:15:50.080
You're...

